  3.812295290351039*^9, 
  3.8122953370709243`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"228f7333-5ee2-42f6-8c64-\
cd89b0184dcb"],

Cell["\<\
So, I am assuming that in fact attribute in table for India States is for \
liters of wine... If I had not assumed this, we could rescale data since in a \
bottle of wine one finds about 13% alcohol. \
\>", "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.808566859193138*^9, 3.808566888203602*^9}, {
  3.808567182247361*^9, 3.80856719813487*^9}, {3.8085675216206*^9, 
