d505a7754b24"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "I will assume it to be per 10,000,000 people based on [",
 ButtonBox["Our World in Data",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/cardiovascular-disease-death-\
rates"], None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/cardiovascular-disease-death-rates"],
 "] where 283 per 100,000 die in India, or 2,830 per 1,000,000 or 28,300 per \
10,000,000, so producing numbers of the order of magnitude presented in the \
table!"
}], "Subitem",
