Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Let us now calculate value for attribute \"number of total deaths due to \
alcohol consumption (column 4, Table 1), and number of deaths from liver \
disease (column 6, Table 1)\". \
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.812297457138629*^9, 3.81229747757699*^9}, {
  3.812700095351205*^9, 
  3.812700123092333*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f4b40b5b-bf1c-4b2c-9cda-\
3f6eede3cc80"],

Cell["\<\
In the data available there is no number of total deaths due to alcohol \
consumption and no number of fatal liver disease, so we will handle as if \
they were missing data, using averages from Sheet 1. However, when using data \
to fill missing data:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.808570086570114*^9, 3.808570127646222*^9}, {
  3.80857015974457*^9, 3.8085701692108183`*^9}, {3.808634315164513*^9, 
  3.80863440913405*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1be1a08b-4bca-4a88-b450-\
56bd191464d1"],

Cell["\<\
one should aim at using original data, to avoid propagating errors caused by \
generating new data from corrupted data that had already been handled. C. \
Shah [TB] has done that generating the value 750 for death in India. That \
however calculates the average considering that deaths in Israel are -834. \
Impossible!\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.808570086570114*^9, 3.808570127646222*^9}, {
  3.80857015974457*^9, 3.8085701692108183`*^9}, {3.808634315164513*^9, 
  3.808634349897189*^9}, {3.808634407840815*^9, 3.808634461916585*^9}, {
  3.80863450885677*^9, 3.808634579221771*^9}, {3.80863462800757*^9, 
  3.808634818342801*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"eac12707-9a93-4137-a579-\
128837656900"],

Cell["\<\
In this case, we could either consider this value for deaths in Israel to be \
zero (which is a better estimate), or simply avoid this value in the produced \
average. I decide to avoid it:\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.808570086570114*^9, 3.808570127646222*^9}, {
   3.80857015974457*^9, 3.8085701692108183`*^9}, {3.808634315164513*^9, 
   3.808634349897189*^9}, {3.808634407840815*^9, 3.808634461916585*^9}, {
   3.80863450885677*^9, 3.8086345106024113`*^9}, 3.8086346974633102`*^9, {
   3.80863482439406*^9, 3.8086348828274603`*^9}, {3.812297419530209*^9, 
   3.812297424863138*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"50fe0840-6b79-4884-a58f-\
07fef3f0d5ca"]
}, Open  ]],

